## Entity Relationships

### Primary Relationship Types

#### 1. Composition Relationships (HAS-A)
```
System HAS-A InfrastructureLayer
System HAS-A ApplicationLayer
System HAS-A ProcessLayer

InfrastructureLayer HAS-A ContainerInfrastructure
InfrastructureLayer HAS-A PackageInfrastructure
InfrastructureLayer HAS-A DatabaseInfrastructure

ApplicationLayer HAS-A AshFramework
ApplicationLayer HAS-A SystemModules

ProcessLayer HAS-A ValidationProcesses
ProcessLayer HAS-A InstallationProcesses
ProcessLayer HAS-A TestingProcesses
```

#### 2. Dependency Relationships (DEPENDS-ON)
```
ApplicationLayer DEPENDS-ON InfrastructureLayer
ProcessLayer DEPENDS-ON ApplicationLayer
TestingProcesses DEPENDS-ON ValidationProcesses

AshFramework DEPENDS-ON PostgreSQLServer
SystemModules DEPENDS-ON NixPackageManager
Container DEPENDS-ON DockerImage

Resource DEPENDS-ON Domain
API DEPENDS-ON Resource
```

#### 3. Execution Relationships (EXECUTES)
```
CoreModule EXECUTES ValidationProcesses
CoreModule EXECUTES InstallationProcesses
CoreModule EXECUTES TestingProcesses

PreflightModule EXECUTES SystemValidation
InstallationModule EXECUTES AshSetup
TestingModule EXECUTES ComprehensiveTesting

Container EXECUTES ValidationScript
Container EXECUTES InstallationScript
Container EXECUTES TestScript
```

#### 4. Communication Relationships (COMMUNICATES-WITH)
```
CoreModule COMMUNICATES-WITH PreflightModule
CoreModule COMMUNICATES-WITH InstallationModule
CoreModule COMMUNICATES-WITH TestingModule

SystemModules COMMUNICATES-WITH DockerModule
TestingModule COMMUNICATES-WITH ValidationModule
ExecutionModule COMMUNICATES-WITH Container
```

#### 5. Data Flow Relationships (FLOWS-TO)
```
UserInput FLOWS-TO CoreModule
CoreModule FLOWS-TO TargetModule
ValidationResults FLOWS-TO CoreModule
TestResults FLOWS-TO ReportGeneration

ConfigurationData FLOWS-TO InstallationProcess
LogData FLOWS-TO MonitoringSystem
MetricsData FLOWS-TO PerformanceAnalysis
```

### Relationship Constraints

#### Cardinality Constraints
```
System : InfrastructureLayer = 1:1
System : ApplicationLayer = 1:1
InfrastructureLayer : ContainerInfrastructure = 1:1
ApplicationLayer : AshFramework = 1:1
AshFramework : Domain = 1:12
Domain : Resource = 1:N
Container : Process = 1:1
```

#### Temporal Constraints
```
ValidationProcesses PRECEDES InstallationProcesses
InstallationProcesses PRECEDES TestingProcesses
SystemValidation PRECEDES AshSetup
DependencyInstallation PRECEDES ProjectGeneration
DatabaseSetup PRECEDES ResourceGeneration
```

#### Conditional Constraints
```
IF TestingMode = "ash-only" THEN Execute AshOnlyTesting
IF ValidationFails THEN HALT InstallationProcess
IF ContainerUnavailable THEN FAIL Operation
IF CriticalTestFails THEN ABORT Deployment
```

