## Behavioral Patterns

### Execution Patterns

#### 1. Request-Response Pattern
```
RequestResponsePattern
├── Trigger: UserInput
├── Process: ArgumentParsing → ModeSelection → ModuleExecution
├── Response: SuccessResult | ErrorResult
└── Termination: SystemExit(ExitCode)
```

#### 2. Validation-Before-Action Pattern
```
ValidationBeforeActionPattern
├── Trigger: OperationRequest
├── Process: PreValidation → MainOperation → PostValidation
├── Constraint: MainOperation ONLY IF PreValidation = Success
└── Cleanup: ResourceCleanup ON ANY Termination
```

#### 3. Container-Isolated-Execution Pattern
```
ContainerIsolatedExecutionPattern
├── Preparation: ScriptGeneration → ContainerSetup
├── Execution: ContainerStart → ScriptExecution → ResultCapture
├── Cleanup: ContainerStop → ResourceCleanup
└── SafetyConstraint: NO DirectHostSystemAccess
```

#### 4. Progressive-Testing Pattern
```
ProgressiveTestingPattern
├── Level1: CoreFunctionality (ash-only)
├── Level2: FeatureCoverage (ash-coverage)
├── Level3: LiveOperations (ash-live)
├── Level4: ProductionReadiness (ash-production)
└── Constraint: Level(N) REQUIRES Success(Level(N-1))
```

### State Transition Patterns

#### 1. System Lifecycle
```
SystemLifecycle
├── States: Uninitialized → Validated → Configured → Tested → Ready
├── Transitions:
│   ├── Uninitialized → Validated [PreflightSuccess]
│   ├── Validated → Configured [InstallationSuccess]
│   ├── Configured → Tested [TestingSuccess]
│   └── Tested → Ready [ValidationSuccess]
└── FailureTransitions: ANY → Error [OperationFailure]
```

#### 2. Container Lifecycle
```
ContainerLifecycle
├── States: NotCreated → Created → Running → Completed → Destroyed
├── Transitions:
│   ├── NotCreated → Created [ImageAvailable]
│   ├── Created → Running [ExecutionStart]
│   ├── Running → Completed [ExecutionFinish]
│   └── Completed → Destroyed [CleanupTrigger]
└── ErrorTransitions: Running → Failed [ExecutionError]
```

#### 3. Validation Lifecycle
```
ValidationLifecycle
├── States: Pending → InProgress → Passed → Failed
├── Transitions:
│   ├── Pending → InProgress [ValidationStart]
│   ├── InProgress → Passed [AllChecksPass]
│   └── InProgress → Failed [AnyCheckFails]
└── RetryPattern: Failed → Pending [UserRetry]
```

### Error Handling Patterns

#### 1. Graceful Degradation Pattern
```
GracefulDegradationPattern
├── Detection: ErrorOccurrence
├── Assessment: CriticalityEvaluation
├── Response:
│   ├── Critical → ImmediateHalt
│   ├── Warning → ContinueWithLogging
│   └── Info → ContinueNormally
└── Recovery: CleanupResources → UserNotification
```

#### 2. Resource Cleanup Pattern
```
ResourceCleanupPattern
├── Trigger: ProcessTermination | ErrorOccurrence
├── Resources:
│   ├── TempFiles → Delete
│   ├── Containers → Stop + Remove
│   ├── Networks → Disconnect
│   └── Processes → Terminate
└── Verification: ResourceCleanupValidation
```

