### Data Transformation Rules

#### Input Transformation
```
UserArguments → ParsedArguments → ValidatedOptions
ConfigurationFiles → ParsedConfig → MergedConfiguration
EnvironmentVariables → SanitizedEnvironment → RuntimeContext
```

#### Processing Transformation
```
SystemState → ValidationResults → ValidationReport
InstallationPhases → InstallationState → ProgressReport
TestExecution → TestResults → ComprehensiveReport
```

#### Output Transformation
```
InternalResults → FormattedOutput → UserDisplay
ProcessingData → StructuredLogs → AuditTrail
ValidationState → ReportData → MarkdownReport
```

### Data Flow Constraints

#### Security Constraints
```
SensitiveData MUST BE RedactedInLogs
PasswordData MUST BE EncryptedAtRest
TemporaryData MUST BE SecurelyDeleted
UserInput MUST BE ValidatedBeforeProcessing
```

#### Quality Constraints
```
AllData MUST BE Validated
LogData MUST BE Structured
ReportData MUST BE Comprehensive
MetricData MUST BE Accurate
```

#### Performance Constraints
```
DataTransformation MUST BE Efficient
LargeDataSets MUST BE StreamProcessed
MemoryUsage MUST BE Bounded
NetworkTransfer MUST BE Minimized
```

