## State Machine Ontology

### Core State Machines

#### 1. System Operation State Machine
```
SystemOperationStateMachine
├── States:
│   ├── Idle
│   ├── ArgumentParsing
│   ├── ModeValidation
│   ├── ModuleExecution
│   ├── ResultProcessing
│   └── Termination
├── Events:
│   ├── UserCommand
│   ├── ValidationComplete
│   ├── ExecutionComplete
│   ├── ErrorOccurred
│   └── ForceTermination
└── Guards:
    ├── ValidArguments?
    ├── SupportedMode?
    ├── ResourcesAvailable?
    └── SafetyConstraintsMet?
```

#### 2. Container Execution State Machine
```
ContainerExecutionStateMachine
├── States:
│   ├── ImageDiscovery
│   ├── ContainerCreation
│   ├── ScriptInjection
│   ├── ExecutionRunning
│   ├── ResultCapture
│   └── Cleanup
├── Events:
│   ├── ImageFound
│   ├── ContainerReady
│   ├── ScriptInjected
│   ├── ExecutionStarted
│   ├── ExecutionCompleted
│   └── CleanupTriggered
└── Actions:
    ├── CreateContainer
    ├── InjectScript
    ├── StartExecution
    ├── CaptureOutput
    └── RemoveContainer
```

#### 3. Validation State Machine
```
ValidationStateMachine
├── States:
│   ├── PreValidation
│   ├── SystemChecks
│   ├── DependencyChecks
│   ├── SecurityChecks
│   ├── ValidationComplete
│   └── ValidationFailed
├── Events:
│   ├── ValidationRequested
│   ├── CheckPassed
│   ├── CheckFailed
│   ├── AllChecksPassed
│   └── CriticalFailure
└── Data:
    ├── CheckResults
    ├── ErrorMessages
    ├── WarningMessages
    └── RecommendedActions
```

### State Machine Composition

#### Hierarchical Composition
```
SystemOperationStateMachine
├── CONTAINS ContainerExecutionStateMachine
└── CONTAINS ValidationStateMachine

ModuleExecution
├── DELEGATES TO ValidationStateMachine
└── DELEGATES TO ContainerExecutionStateMachine
```

#### Parallel Composition
```
PARALLEL {
  ValidationStateMachine,
  LoggingStateMachine,
  MonitoringStateMachine
}
```

### State Machine Invariants

#### Safety Invariants
```
ALWAYS (ContainerState = Running) → (HostSystem = Protected)
ALWAYS (ValidationState = Failed) → (Installation = Blocked)
ALWAYS (CriticalError = True) → (Operation = Terminated)
```

#### Liveness Invariants
```
EVENTUALLY (ValidationRequested) → (ValidationComplete ∨ ValidationFailed)
EVENTUALLY (ContainerStarted) → (ContainerCompleted ∨ ContainerFailed)
EVENTUALLY (OperationStarted) → (OperationCompleted ∨ OperationFailed)
```

