└── Quality Metrics
    ├── ErrorRate
    ├── SuccessRate
    ├── Availability
    └── Reliability
```

#### 2. Performance Targets
```
PerformanceTargets
├── ResponseTimeLimits
│   ├── PreflightValidation ≤ 300 seconds
│   ├── InstallationProcess ≤ 1800 seconds
│   ├── AshOnlyTesting ≤ 180 seconds
│   └── ProductionTesting ≤ 900 seconds
├── ThroughputRequirements
│   ├── ConcurrentOperations ≥ 100
│   ├── DatabaseTransactions ≥ 1000/second
│   └── APIRequests ≥ 500/second
└── ResourceLimits
    ├── MemoryUsage ≤ 8GB
    ├── CPUUtilization ≤ 80%
    └── DiskSpace ≤ 50GB
```

#### 3. Performance Patterns
```
PerformancePatterns
├── OptimizationPatterns
│   ├── CachingStrategy
│   ├── ConnectionPooling
│   ├── ParallelProcessing
│   └── LazyLoading
├── ScalingPatterns
│   ├── HorizontalScaling
│   ├── VerticalScaling
│   ├── LoadBalancing
│   └── AutoScaling
└── MonitoringPatterns
    ├── RealTimeMonitoring
    ├── PerformanceProfiling
    ├── BottleneckDetection
    └── CapacityPlanning
```

### Performance Relationships

#### Performance Dependencies
```
SystemPerformance DEPENDS-ON InfrastructurePerformance
ApplicationPerformance DEPENDS-ON SystemPerformance
UserExperience DEPENDS-ON ApplicationPerformance

DatabasePerformance AFFECTS OverallSystemPerformance
NetworkPerformance AFFECTS DistributedOperations
ContainerPerformance AFFECTS ExecutionTime
```

#### Performance Trade-offs
```
Security ⟷ Performance
Reliability ⟷ Performance
Scalability ⟷ Consistency
Availability ⟷ PartitionTolerance
```

### Performance Constraints

#### Hard Constraints
```
MaxExecutionTime ≤ ConfiguredTimeout
MaxMemoryUsage ≤ SystemMemoryLimit
MaxCPUUsage ≤ 100% × AvailableCores
MaxDiskUsage ≤ AvailableDiskSpace
```

#### Soft Constraints
```
PreferredResponseTime ≤ UserExpectation
OptimalThroughput ≥ ExpectedLoad
SustainableResourceUsage ≤ 70% × Capacity
AcceptableErrorRate ≤ 0.1%
```

