### Operational Relationships

#### Service Level Relationships
```
Service PROVIDES Capability TO User UNDER SLA
MonitoringService PROVIDES HealthStatus TO Operations UNDER AvailabilitySLA
BackupService PROVIDES DataRecovery TO Business UNDER RecoveryTimeSLA
SecurityService PROVIDES Protection TO System UNDER SecuritySLA
```

#### Dependency Relationships
```
ApplicationService DEPENDS-ON DatabaseService
DatabaseService DEPENDS-ON InfrastructureService
MonitoringService DEPENDS-ON NetworkService
BackupService DEPENDS-ON StorageService
```

#### Communication Relationships
```
OperationalRole COMMUNICATES-WITH System VIA Interface
Administrator COMMUNICATES-WITH MonitoringSystem VIA Dashboard
Operator COMMUNICATES-WITH DeploymentSystem VIA CLI
SecurityOfficer COMMUNICATES-WITH SecuritySystem VIA AlertingSystem
```

### Operational Patterns

#### 1. Continuous Operation Pattern
```
ContinuousOperationPattern
├── HealthMonitoring: ContinuousSystemHealthChecks
├── AutomaticRecovery: SelfHealingCapabilities
├── LoadBalancing: DistributedSystemLoad
├── Redundancy: FailoverMechanisms
└── Maintenance: ZeroDowntimeMaintenance
```

#### 2. Incident Management Pattern
```
IncidentManagementPattern
├── Detection: AutomaticIncidentDetection
├── Classification: SeverityAndImpactAssessment
├── Response: EscalationAndResourceAllocation
├── Resolution: ProblemSolving AndImplementation
├── Recovery: ServiceRestoration AndValidation
└── PostIncident: LessonsLearned AndImprovement
```

#### 3. Change Management Pattern
```
ChangeManagementPattern
├── Planning: ChangeRequest AndImpactAssessment
├── Approval: ChangeAdvisoryBoard Review
├── Implementation: ControlledChangeExecution
├── Verification: ChangeValidation AndTesting
└── Documentation: ChangeRecord AndKnowledgeUpdate
```

### Operational Constraints

#### Service Level Constraints
```
SystemAvailability ≥ 99.9%
ResponseTime ≤ ServiceLevelAgreement
RecoveryTime ≤ RecoveryTimeObjective
DataLoss ≤ RecoveryPointObjective
```

#### Process Constraints
```
ChangeRequests MUST BE ApprovedBeforeImplementation
IncidentResponse MUST BE InitiatedWithinSLATime
BackupProcedures MUST BE ExecutedDaily
SecurityPatches MUST BE AppliedWithinComplianceWindow
```

#### Resource Constraints
```
OperationalStaffing ≥ MinimumRequiredStaff
ToolLicenses ≥ OperationalRequirements
InfrastructureCapacity ≥ ExpectedLoad + Buffer
BudgetAllocation ≥ OperationalExpenses
```

